{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio"},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents9OUDSRadioV","title":"OUDSRadio","symbolKind":"struct","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSRadio","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Structure"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradio"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" proposes layout to add in your views a lonely radio, without labels, texts nor icons radios components","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a radio with additional texts and icon, prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio\/init(isOn:accessibilityLabel:isError:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio\/body"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties","title":"Instance Properties"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio\/Vi